{"tid":1295600,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"幫香港警察設計新Logo／宣傳物有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-07-08T05:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T09:45:11.000Z","uid":52123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8366aea71088af373f43e88579b9eb5e268d35","tid":1295600,"uid":52123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uSRLST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uSRLST.jpg&h=d473fff5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmNZajA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmNZajA.jpg&h=92b4c99a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />苦中作樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d811c8c3d3ac11d911326da47fdf9bfaa01e89e1","tid":1295600,"uid":92859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手推上熱門<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［重要］區議會選舉招募各路人馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295057\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295057</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，光復行動冇可能每日都做<br />\n好似屯門公園搞到今日咁烏煙瘴氣區議員責無旁貸<br />\n要清洗屯門公園始終要由根源做起<br />\n所以除左投立法會外<br />\n都請記得投票區議會踢走自動當選建制派<br />\n<br />\n唔好再俾建制派霸哂啲議席<br />\n就算唔係參選都可以做提名人，義工，助選團<br />\n行出第一步拒絕自動當選！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總台TG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictCouncil2019&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4Vz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=fd7609dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictCouncil2019</a><br />\n</span></span><br />\n登記左做選民既全部入group<br />\n急需大量提名人，義工助選團，Design等職位<br />\n入group後右下角Discuss入公頻搵各區admin<br />\n<br />\n要對抗黑警濫權一定要有議員抗衡<br />\n否則只會一直任人魚肉"},{"pid":"296fb25438a7df4bca0aa31368522